<!-- 
  NOTE: This is a READ-ONLY file in actual projects.
  
  The AI cannot directly modify this file.
  Instead, it uses:
  - alive-add-dependency("package-name@version")
  - alive-remove-dependency("package-name")
  
  These tools:
  1. Validate the package exists
  2. Check for conflicts
  3. Update package.json
  4. Run npm/bun install
  5. Update lock files
-->
